txt.en: A bounty notice asks you to seek out a goblin that has been seen lurking around the Cabed Rhimdath in Misthallow.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest.</rgb>
You remove the completed bounty from the Limlók bounty board, feeling a sense of accomplishment in your efforts to protect the Langflood.
Defeat all goblins in the Cabed Rhimdath.

The bounty notice reads:

'Goblins run rampant in Misthallow! By order of Skarding Wargsbane, all goblins in Misthallow are to be found and defeated immediately! A particularly troublesome goblin has been recently spotted taking refuge in Cabed Rhimdath. A reward to any who can defeat it with haste!'

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest.</rgb>
You should return to Limlók and remove the completed bounty from the bounty board.
Examine the bounty and defeat goblins in the Cabed Rhimdath
Return to Limlók and remove the completed bounty
Bounty: Goblin in the Cabed Rhimdath
